# coder scaletest

Run a scale test against the Coder API
## Usage
```console
coder scaletest [flags]
```

## Subcommands
| Name |   Purpose |
| ---- |   ----- |
| <code>cleanup</code> | Cleanup any orphaned scaletest resources |
| <code>create-workspaces</code> | Creates many workspaces and waits for them to be ready |
